### ✅ Corrected (Actual Syntax with Workarounds)

```elixir
# WORKS - Uses the real DSL with workarounds
import EngineSystem.Engine.DSL  # Direct import as workaround

defengine(KeyValueStore, version: "1.0") do  # Explicit parentheses required
